    <h1>SOFTWARE AS A SERVICE</h1>
    <p>
        Why should you operate a power plant, when all you need is electric power? Should you have to deploy,
        manage and update all the systems you use? Why not just <b>use what you really need</b>, the software!
    </p>
    <p>
        Software as a Service (SaaS) is based on the belief that <b>IT shouldn't be a burden</b>,
        but rather a <b>precious utility</b>.
        Whether you want to reduce the strain on your IT staff, or maybe just get access to top business software
        without the need for an IT department, SaaS may be the way to go.
    </p>
    <p>
        Here at Hive Solutions we have people who <b>know the players</b> in the market, and can help you pick and adapt the best solution for your specific needs.
        Bear in mind that SaaS is not a silver bullet, and that we can help you understand if it truly fits your needs.
    </p>
